<p>Reports incorrect JBoss-specific XML deployment descriptors:</p>

<ul>
  <li><code>jboss-web.xml</code></li>
  <li><code>jboss-app.xml</code></li>
  <li><code>jboss.xml</code></li>
</ul>

<p>Some of the reported issues are:</p>

<ul>
  <li>References to non-instantiable classes</li>
  <li>References to classes that do not extend a required class</li>
  <li>Empty tag and attribute values</li>
  <li>Tags that do not include required children tags or attributes</li>
  <li>Tags that define objects with duplicate names</li>
</ul>
